    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start for the students. I also want to address the pushback from some legal scholars who argue this is basically just \"judicial activism.\" How would you explain their perspective to the class so they understand why some people think it's a flawed way to interpret the Constitution?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
